(829, 117, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"f16ddfa\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"layout\":\"full_width\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9a2a527\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7b3fd63\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"<h1 class=\\\"entry-title\\\">How to Set up QR Code Ordering for Your Restaurant<\\/h1>\",\"align\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"ca0156e\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"cc4f20f\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"5cd255a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>QR code ordering is a great solution for restaurants that want to offer customers a way to order food from where they\\u2019re sitting. But if you\\u2019re a restaurant owner, you may be wondering:<\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p><ol><li>Is QR code ordering worth setting up in my dine-in restaurant?<\\/li><li>If so, how do I get started with QR code ordering?<\\/li><\\/ol>\",\"text_color\":\"#7A7A7AF7\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"6283dcc\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"0fda906\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"1f2ffaf\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"<span style=\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600;\\\">What is QR code ordering?<\\/span>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"5372b1a\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"c87def0\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7f073e3\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>This <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/orderable.com\\/blog\\/wordpress-restaurant-menu\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\" data-type=\\\"post\\\" data-id=\\\"5273\\\">online menu<\\/a> can be on an app ordering page, <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/orderable.com\\/blog\\/online-ordering-system-for-your-small-business\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\" data-type=\\\"post\\\" data-id=\\\"3355\\\">online ordering system<\\/a>, or digital menu on your website.<\\/p><p>Once ordered, restaurant staff will then fulfill and deliver the order to the customer\\u2019s table.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"2e5ac6f\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"layout\":\"full_width\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"e1a69b6\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"915e79e\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress3\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/fb1.png\",\"id\":109,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"fab4d3a\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3546719\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"cc86446\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>This way of dine-in ordering is an alternative to restaurants having a printed menu. Instead, customers are given a different ordering experience that requires less staff contact.<\\/p><p>QR code ordering became a popular way for customers to dine in during the pandemic. But since then, restaurants have adopted this technique because it has a host of benefits, which we\\u2019ll outline next.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"930b568\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"6c08186\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"fb2cfa3\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"<span style=\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600;\\\">Why use QR code ordering for your restaurant?<\\/span>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"721043a\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f6c3e2f\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"1c64be4\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>QR code ordering isn\\u2019t just for pandemic times. There\\u2019s a reason why restaurants are still using this dining experience today.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"92f2a18\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"58c6e9a\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"6527d45\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"<h3>Increased restaurant efficiency<\\/h3>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"695dcff\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f42807f\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9fb8df5\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>With QR code ordering, customers can view the QR code menu, place orders, and make payments quickly and efficiently. Because of this, it reduces the need for waitstaff to attend to customers in person.<\\/p><p>Not only does this make your restaurant more efficient, but it also increases table turnover. Wait times are reduced because customers order in their own time, so restaurants can serve more customers in a shorter amount of time.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"9548948\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f5482ff\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"d194acd\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress3\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/fb2.png\",\"id\":110,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"1d297c0\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f5a427b\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f3ec02c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<h3>Improved customer experience<\\/h3><p>If your customers prefer a speedy, contact-free dining experience, \\nthen QR code ordering will improve their experience of dining with you.<\\/p><p>Customers will also have all the information they need to make a \\ndecision that\\u2019s right for them. Your online menu will have room to \\ninclude <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/orderable.com\\/blog\\/custom-woocommerce-product-labels\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" data-type=\\\"post\\\" data-id=\\\"5588\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\">dietary labels<\\/a>, nutritional information, allergens, and more.<\\/p><p>Convenience is key, and with contactless ordering, customers will be \\nable to take their time ordering on their mobile devices. Without the \\nneed for constant restaurant staff contact, they\\u2019ll be able to enjoy a <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/orderable.com\\/blog\\/online-ordering-system-for-takeaway\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" data-type=\\\"post\\\" data-id=\\\"5438\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\">takeout-like experience<\\/a> within your establishment.<\\/p><h3>Accuracy of orders<\\/h3><p>When ordering from your online menu, there\\u2019s less chance for mistakes\\n to happen. Orders are delivered right to the kitchen, so they won\\u2019t be \\nlost in translation.<\\/p><p>Any additional requirements like allergens and dietary preferences \\nwill also be communicated so kitchen staff has all the information they \\nneed to make the best meal possible.<\\/p><h3>Upselling and cross-selling opportunities<\\/h3><p>When using QR code ordering, customers will have access to your full \\nonline menu. If using an online ordering platform or app, you\\u2019ll also \\nhave the means to <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/iconicwp.com\\/blog\\/how-to-cross-sell-in-woocommerce\\/?_ics=1680074690287&amp;irclickid=~625VUYNIMIPVWY1XZ05-2SULBHLMINEzokilmcda~2RQMGDsigc5\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\">cross-sell or upsell<\\/a> your customers.<\\/p><p>\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n<\\/p><p>Instead of relying on wait staff to promote sides, special dishes, and desserts, you can do it in your QR menu.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
