(919, 124, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"a7cbf1d\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"6880585\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"74f1837\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<h1 class=\\\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\\\">How to Prepare Your Hotel Buffet for the Holiday Season<\\/h1>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"1aa0fc6\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9ffb41f\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"c1f8437\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.rosseto.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/09\\/christmas-dinner-g3f91e68bd_1920-1024x678.jpg.webp\",\"id\":\"\",\"size\":\"\",\"source\":\"url\",\"alt\":\"\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"ab1821d\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"111d27d\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"d4ee4f8\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<h2>The holiday season is right around the corner, which means now is the time to start preparing and making sure you have all of the hotel buffet equipment you need. This special time of year comes with its own set of unique demands on food and beverage managers across the industry, heightening the need for creating remarkable experiences for each guest.<\\/h2><p>Thankfully, there\\u2019s a way to create a fantastic holiday buffet for hotel visitors worldwide. This article will provide you with all of the information you need to set up your holiday buffet using the latest styles and designs in buffet equipment.<\\/p><h2><strong>How to create a Memorable Holiday Buffet?<br \\/><\\/strong><\\/h2><p>When looking to create unforgettable hotel buffets this holiday season, food and beverage managers across the industry are presented with several different challenges.<\\/p><h3>Increasing Numbers<\\/h3><p>The holiday season is a busy time of year for everyone. Much of the hospitality industry sees its highest numbers in terms of customers during the holidays.<\\/p><p>While food and beverage managers are busy year-round, this special time of year means handling even more guests, adjusting schedules, and planning ahead to ensure the restaurant buffet equipment can handle these exciting times.<\\/p><h3>Keeping Everyone Safe<\\/h3><p>The hospitality industry remains under scrutiny regarding health and safety regulations following the COVID-19 pandemic. Guests and staff both want to know that hotel buffet equipment can help protect them from the spread of infectious viruses.<\\/p><p>With increased numbers of guests and staff servers, food and beverage managers have to remain vigilant with health and safety precautions.<\\/p><h3>Creating New Menu Items<\\/h3><p>A new holiday season means guests who anticipate new and exciting menu items to match. Changing out the menus with seasonal rotations is just one aspect food and beverage managers face, but creating inspiring options for holiday offerings is a whole different ball game.<\\/p><p>Sometimes, these new holiday menu items can increase food costs, so it is up to food and beverage managers to find affordable buffet equipment to help offset some of these costs.<\\/p><h3>Paying Attention to the Details<\\/h3><p>Creating a holiday buffet that won\\u2019t soon be forgotten is a challenge in and of itself for food and beverage managers, but finding the time to plan and execute an event like this just adds to the stress of it all.<\\/p><p>Guests have extraordinarily high expectations for any celebration around the holidays. It\\u2019s not just about the food offerings when it comes to a holiday buffet; it\\u2019s about every little detail.<\\/p><h2>The Holiday Buffet Solution<\\/h2><p>Thankfully, the experts at Rosseto are here to help you create a holiday buffet that keeps your guests coming back to see what\\u2019s in store each year.<\\/p><p>You can ensure your guests have a magical evening they won\\u2019t soon forget by planning ahead of time, having the best chef, and sticking to a theme.<\\/p><h3>Planning Ahead<\\/h3><p>Planning is the key to successful event management during the holidays. This time of year is a hectic time for anyone, but especially so for food and beverage managers scrambling to get their holiday buffets in line.<\\/p><p>Rather than waiting until the last moment, make sure you take the time now to plan ahead for your buffets to ensure that holiday season hotel visitors are able to enjoy a buffet they deserve.<\\/p><p>Check that your current hotel buffet equipment can handle the volume of visitors you\\u2019re projecting this holiday season. If not, now is the time to start ordering your affordable buffet equipment to get you through the season.<\\/p><h3><strong>Having the Best Chef<\\/strong><\\/h3><p>When it comes to the holidays, no gesture is too large. To make a holiday buffet special, you can have a chef host a one-of-a-kind <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.rosseto.com\\/blog\\/action-stations-the-future-of-event-buffets\\/\\\" data-mil=\\\"49682\\\">action station<\\/a>.<\\/p><p>You can captivate your attendees with dinner and a show with the help of thoughtfully placed action stations. Here, your chef can keep the excitement going while working in front of everyone.<\\/p><h3>\\u00a0<\\/h3>\",\"text_color\":\"#000000\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"4001508\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"4cccb58\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"5b34720\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress3\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/my.jpeg\",\"id\":126,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"4393c60\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"2f23009\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"e9a3cf3\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"shortcode\":\"[social_button type=\\\"twitter\\\"]\\n[social_button type=\\\"facebook\\\"]\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"shortcode\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
