ail.<\\/p><h2>The Holiday Buffet Solution<\\/h2><p>Thankfully, the experts at Rosseto are here to help you create a holiday buffet that keeps your guests coming back to see what\\u2019s in store each year.<\\/p><p>You can ensure your guests have a magical evening they won\\u2019t soon forget by planning ahead of time, having the best chef, and sticking to a theme.<\\/p><h3>Planning Ahead<\\/h3><p>Planning is the key to successful event management during the holidays. This time of year is a hectic time for anyone, but especially so for food and beverage managers scrambling to get their holiday buffets in line.<\\/p><p>Rather than waiting until the last moment, make sure you take the time now to plan ahead for your buffets to ensure that holiday season hotel visitors are able to enjoy a buffet they deserve.<\\/p><p>Check that your current hotel buffet equipment can handle the volume of visitors you\\u2019re projecting this holiday season. If not, now is the time to start ordering your affordable buffet equipment to get you through the season.<\\/p><h3><strong>Having the Best Chef<\\/strong><\\/h3><p>When it comes to the holidays, no gesture is too large. To make a holiday buffet special, you can have a chef host a one-of-a-kind <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.rosseto.com\\/blog\\/action-stations-the-future-of-event-buffets\\/\\\" data-mil=\\\"49682\\\">action station<\\/a>.<\\/p><p>You can captivate your attendees with dinner and a show with the help of thoughtfully placed action stations. Here, your chef can keep the excitement going while working in front of everyone.<\\/p><h3>\\u00a0<\\/h3>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
