(114, 1, '2023-03-29 08:44:56', '2023-03-29 08:44:56', '<style>/*! elementor - v3.11.5 - 14-03-2023 */\n.elementor-heading-title{padding:0;margin:0;line-height:1}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title[class*=elementor-size-]>a{color:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-small{font-size:15px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-medium{font-size:19px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-large{font-size:29px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xl{font-size:39px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xxl{font-size:59px}</style><h2><h1>Six major hospitality industry trends every banquet and food and beverage director needs to know</h1></h2>		\n			<style>/*! elementor - v3.11.5 - 14-03-2023 */\n.elementor-widget-image{text-align:center}.elementor-widget-image a{display:inline-block}.elementor-widget-image a img[src$=\".svg\"]{width:48px}.elementor-widget-image img{vertical-align:middle;display:inline-block}</style>												<img src=\"https://www.rosseto.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Mid-Morning-Buffet-Enhanced-1000x564.jpg.webp\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n		<p>The hospitality industry is constantly evolving to meet the needs and desires of guests and customers. One area that is particularly important for hotels, restaurants, and other hospitality businesses is food presentation and service, especially at buffets. In order to keep up with the latest trends and provide the best possible experience for guests, it is essential for all for those in the hospitality industry to stay up-to-date on the latest hot trends and new and improved serving solutions out there, especially when it comes to utilizing space and creativity in the buffet equipment and serving solutions department.  </p><p>Recently, there have been some f major trends emerging in the hospitality industry, particularly in the area of buffet equipment and serving solutions. </p><h2>Here are 6 of the hottest trends we’re looking at in 2023</h2> <ol><li><strong>Self-service kiosks and digital ordering systems</strong> <br />Using self-service kiosks and digital ordering systems for buffet lines has become increasingly popular in recent years due to developments in technology and the growing demand for contactless service. Covid-19 has given a twist to this section of the buffet and many hotels, restaurants, and shops are turning to the use of self-service kiosks and touchless systems for their buffet lines.  This is handy not only because of the germ-free atmosphere but also because of the benefit of using portion control to cut costs and give the client exact measured portions that are suitable for the venue and the client as well.</li><li><strong>Eco-friendly and sustainable materials</strong><br /><a href=\"https://www.rosseto.com/blog/sustainability-solutions-in-the-food-beverage-industry/\" data-mil=\"50250\">Sustainability</a> is a major trend in the hospitality industry, and this extends to buffet equipment as well. Many businesses are opting for serving solutions made from  sustainable materials. For manufacturers, the key is to use the right materials when manufacturing buffet equipment and serving solutions. In this case, the better the quality of the product, the less chance you will need to replace it in the near future.</li><li><strong>Modern and sleek design<br /></strong> Gone are the days of basic, utilitarian buffet equipment. Today, many businesses are seeking out modern and sleek designs that will help to create a more upscale and sophisticated atmosphere. This includes <a href=\"https://www.rosseto.com/blog/dynamic-serving-solutions-and-easy-to-build-beverage-stations/\" data-mil=\"50250\">serving solutions</a> made from high-quality materials, such as stainless steel and glass, and featuring clean lines and minimalistic designs.</li><li><strong>Equipment for Enhanced food safety and hygiene<br /></strong> With the ongoing concerns around food safety and hygiene, many businesses are focusing on equipment and <a href=\"https://www.rosseto.com/collections/safety/\" data-mil=\"50250\">serving solutions that help to reduce the risk of contamination</a> and the spread of germs. This includes items such as sneeze guards, touchless dispensers, and hands-free utensils.</li><li><strong>Brand Customization</strong><br />Hospitality brands can differentiate themselves from the competition and promote their unique brand by customizing design, materials,and even with navigation. Customized buffet equipment can feature a hotel’s logo, colors, and other branding elements, making it an effective marketing tool to the brand. At the same time creating a unique look, which can make it a talking point among customers and also help create a memorable experience.</li><li><strong>Smart Space Utilization</strong> <br />Utilizing your space – is not a trend but more of a practical solution that also improves customer experience. <a href=\"https://www.rosseto.com/blog/modular-serving-solutions-hospitality-trends/\" data-mil=\"50250\">Buffet equipment</a> that is easy to navigate and well-organized can help improve the overall customer experience. Not to mention when you need to find creative solutions for limited space such as items that elevate your buffet by giving it height. Another key factor for buffet serving solutions equipment is for the products to be stackable. In the storage area, this is a key factor for any manager that does not want to deal with broken equipment and a lack of storage space. Buffet equipment needs to be modular, the same way as it needs to be well designed.</li></ol>		\n															<img src=\"https://www.rosseto.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/IMG_2191-copy-1000x667.jpg.webp\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n		<h2>So what can we expect to see in the future?</h2><p>Based on these current trends, it is likely that 2023 will continue to highlight and emphasize the use of new technology, in order to encourage sustainability and food safety. The pandemic has shown us that predicting trends in the world of hospitality is not easy, and buffet equipment and serving solutions are no different.</p><p>But there are some things that are constant – great products that are built to last and have great design will always be trendy. In addition, we may see an even greater focus on customization and personalization, as businesses look for ways to differentiate themselves and stand out in a competitive market.</p><p>Let our Rosseto experts help you determine what kind of buffet equipment is best for you when revamping your buffet and looking to enhance customer experience at your hotel or restaurant. For procurement managers looking for a vendor for luxury buffet equipment, it is important to keep these trends in mind and seek out suppliers who are able to offer a wide range of options that meet the needs of your business and your guests. You can create a memorable dining experience by using the right equipment and serving solutions.</p><h2>Advantages of quality buffet products</h2><p>There are a number of advantages that can be gained by hotels and restaurants using quality products as part of their serving solutions. One of the most obvious benefits is the enhanced appearance and aesthetic appeal of the buffet line. High-quality equipment and serving solutions can help create a more upscale and sophisticated atmosphere, which can be especially important for luxury hotels and restaurants.</p><p>In addition to their visual appeal, quality products can also provide practical benefits. For example, durable and well-made serving solutions are less likely to break or malfunction, which can save businesses time and money in the long run. Quality products are also more likely to be able to withstand the wear and tear of constant use, making them a worthwhile investment for businesses that rely heavily on buffet service.</p><p>Another advantage of using quality products is the increased food safety and hygiene that they can provide. Items such as sneeze guards and touchless dispensers can help to reduce the risk of contamination and the spread of germs, which is especially important in the current climate. This can not only help to keep guests safe and healthy, but it can also help to protect the reputation of the business.</p><p>Overall, investing in quality products for serving solutions is the smartest decision for businesses in the hospitality industry. While they may come with a higher initial cost, they can provide long-term benefits in terms of appearance, functionality, and food safety.</p><h3>Considering Rossetto as your buffet equipment and serving solutions supplier</h3><p>Rosseto is a leading manufacturer of buffet equipment and serving solutions. We are known for our commitment to top-quality and innovative design. Each Rosseto product is carefully crafted with the needs of the hospitality industry in mind, and the company’s products are highly regarded for their functionality, durability, and aesthetic appeal.</p><p>One of the standout features of Rosseto’s products is its innovative designs. From modern and sleek serving stations to elegant and sophisticated tabletop options, Rosseto has a wide range of products to choose from, all of which are designed to enhance the presentation and food service. Whether you are looking for a buffet station to display a variety of dishes, or a tabletop serving solution to create an intimate dining experience, Rosseto has something that will fit every need., In addition to great designs, Rosseto’s products are also known for their high-quality materials and construction. Whether you choose a product made from stainless steel, glass, or sustainable materials, you can be confident that you are getting a product that is built to last and will provide years of reliable service.</p><p>Rosseto’s products are a fantastic choice for businesses looking for top-quality buffet equipment and serving solutions. With their commitment to innovation and design, Rosseto’s products are sure to impress your guests and enhance the overall dining experience at your establishment.</p>[social_button type=\"twitter\"]\n[social_button type=\"facebook\"]', 'SIX MAJOR HOSPITALITY TRENDS', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'post2', '', '', '2023-03-29 12:35:30', '2023-03-29 12:35:30', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress3/wordpress/?p=114', 0, 'post', '', 0),
