(121, 1, '2023-03-29 08:47:10', '2023-03-29 08:47:10', '<style>/*! elementor - v3.11.5 - 14-03-2023 */\n.elementor-heading-title{padding:0;margin:0;line-height:1}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title[class*=elementor-size-]>a{color:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-small{font-size:15px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-medium{font-size:19px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-large{font-size:29px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xl{font-size:39px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xxl{font-size:59px}</style><h2><h1>Six major hospitality industry trends every banquet and food and beverage director needs to know</h1></h2>		\n			<style>/*! elementor - v3.11.5 - 14-03-2023 */\n.elementor-widget-image{text-align:center}.elementor-widget-image a{display:inline-block}.elementor-widget-image a img[src$=\".svg\"]{width:48px}.elementor-widget-image img{vertical-align:middle;display:inline-block}</style>												<img src=\"https://www.rosseto.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Mid-Morning-Buffet-Enhanced-1000x564.jpg.webp\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n		 <p> </p><section data-id=\"426d6784\" data-element_type=\"section\"> <p>The hospitality industry is constantly evolving to meet the needs and desires of guests and customers. One area that is particularly important for hotels, restaurants, and other hospitality businesses is food presentation and service, especially at buffets. In order to keep up with the latest trends and provide the best possible experience for guests, it is essential for all for those in the hospitality industry to stay up-to-date on the latest hot trends and new and improved serving solutions out there, especially when it comes to utilizing space and creativity in the buffet equipment and serving solutions department.  </p><p>Recently, there have been some f major trends emerging in the hospitality industry, particularly in the area of buffet equipment and serving solutions. </p><h2>Here are 6 of the hottest trends we’re looking at in 2023</h2> <ol><li><strong>Self-service kiosks and digital ordering systems</strong> <br />Using self-service kiosks and digital ordering systems for buffet lines has become increasingly popular in recent years due to developments in technology and the growing demand for contactless service. Covid-19 has given a twist to this section of the buffet and many hotels, restaurants, and shops are turning to the use of self-service kiosks and touchless systems for their buffet lines.  This is handy not only because of the germ-free atmosphere but also because of the benefit of using portion control to cut costs and give the client exact measured portions that are suitable for the venue and the client as well.</li><li><strong>Eco-friendly and sustainable materials</strong><br /><a href=\"https://www.rosseto.com/blog/sustainability-solutions-in-the-food-beverage-industry/\" data-mil=\"50250\">Sustainability</a> is a major trend in the hospitality industry, and this extends to buffet equipment as well. Many businesses are opting for serving solutions made from  sustainable materials. For manufacturers, the key is to use the right materials when manufacturing buffet equipment and serving solutions. In this case, the better the quality of the product, the less chance you will need to replace it in the near future.</li><li><strong>Modern and sleek design<br /></strong> Gone are the days of basic, utilitarian buffet equipment. Today, many businesses are seeking out modern and sleek designs that will help to create a more upscale and sophisticated atmosphere. This includes <a href=\"https://www.rosseto.com/blog/dynamic-serving-solutions-and-easy-to-build-beverage-stations/\" data-mil=\"50250\">serving solutions</a> made from high-quality materials, such as stainless steel and glass, and featuring clean lines and minimalistic designs.</li><li><strong>Equipment for Enhanced food safety and hygiene<br /></strong> With the ongoing concerns around food safety and hygiene, many businesses are focusing on equipment and <a href=\"https://www.rosseto.com/collections/safety/\" data-mil=\"50250\">serving solutions that help to reduce the risk of contamination</a> and the spread of germs. This includes items such as sneeze guards, touchless dispensers, and hands-free utensils.</li><li><strong>Brand Customization</strong><br />Hospitality brands can differentiate themselves from the competition and promote their unique brand by customizing design, materials,and even with navigation. Customized buffet equipment can feature a hotel’s logo, colors, and other branding elements, making it an effective marketing tool to the brand. At the same time creating a unique look, which can make it a talking point among customers and also help create a memorable experience.</li><li><strong>Smart Space Utilization</strong> <br />Utilizing your space – is not a trend but more of a practical solution that also improves customer experience. <a href=\"https://www.rosseto.com/blog/modular-serving-solutions-hospitality-trends/\" data-mil=\"50250\">Buffet equipment</a> that is easy to navigate and well-organized can help improve the overall customer experience. Not to mention when you need to find creative solutions for limited space such as items that elevate your buffet by giving it height. Another key factor for buffet serving solutions equipment is for the products to be stackable. In the storage area, this is a key factor for any manager that does not want to deal with broken equipment and a lack of storage space. Buffet equipment needs to be modular, the same way as it needs to be well designed.</li></ol></section>		\n															<img src=\"https://www.rosseto.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/IMG_2191-copy-1000x667.jpg.webp\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />', 'post2', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '114-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-03-29 08:47:10', '2023-03-29 08:47:10', '', 114, 'http://localhost/wordpress3/wordpress/?p=121', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
