less steel and glass, and featuring clean lines and minimalistic designs.</li><li><strong>Equipment for Enhanced food safety and hygiene<br /></strong> With the ongoing concerns around food safety and hygiene, many businesses are focusing on equipment and <a href=\"https://www.rosseto.com/collections/safety/\" data-mil=\"50250\">serving solutions that help to reduce the risk of contamination</a> and the spread of germs. This includes items such as sneeze guards, touchless dispensers, and hands-free utensils.</li><li><strong>Brand Customization</strong><br />Hospitality brands can differentiate themselves from the competition and promote their unique brand by customizing design, materials,and even with navigation. Customized buffet equipment can feature a hotel’s logo, colors, and other branding elements, making it an effective marketing tool to the brand. At the same time creating a unique look, which can make it a talking point among customers and also help create a memorable experience.</li><li><strong>Smart Space Utilization</strong> <br />Utilizing your space – is not a trend but more of a practical solution that also improves customer experience. <a href=\"https://www.rosseto.com/blog/modular-serving-solutions-hospitality-trends/\" data-mil=\"50250\">Buffet equipment</a> that is easy to navigate and well-organized can help improve the overall customer experience. Not to mention when you need to find creative solutions for limited space such as items that elevate your buffet by giving it height. Another key factor for buffet serving solutions equipment is for the products to be stackable. In the storage area, this is a key factor for any manager that does not want to deal with broken equipment and a lack of storage space. Buffet equipment needs to be modular, the same way as it needs to be well designed.</li></ol></section>		\n															<img src=\"https://www.rosseto.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/IMG_2191-copy-1000x667.jpg.webp\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />', 'post2', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '114-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-03-29 08:47:10', '2023-03-29 08:47:10', '', 114, 'http://localhost/wordpress3/wordpress/?p=122', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
